":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-004","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"The other day, the idol group that made Aya-chan strive to become an idol had their last concert.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-005","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"This is a photo of Pastel＊Palettes and that idol group together.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-006","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"See? Aya-chan's smile is lovely, isn't it?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-008","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Aya-chan was really depressed until she got to meet the leader of this idol group.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-009","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"The break up of the idol group that made her want to become an idol...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-010","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"It's basically as if the thing that gave her this dream suddenly ceased to exist. It's only natural that she felt depressed.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"sad01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-011","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"... But that doesn't mean it's okay for her to be rehearsing absent-mindedly.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-012","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Well, everything worked out this time, so I guess it's okay.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-013","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Oh, that reminds me, when we were talking about this...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-014","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Maya-chan told us about why she started to play the drums. She said that she heard a certain drummer play, and began to learn out of admiration for this person.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"smile01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-015","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"After hearing this, it made me think...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-016","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"It was me who asked her to join Pastel＊Palettes, and if she hadn't been a drummer, we wouldn't be the group that we are now...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"serious01","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-017","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"The drummer that Maya-chan happened to hear that day, connected to Pastel＊Palettes as we know it.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf05","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-018","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Fufu, isn't this fascinating?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"smile02","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-019","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Have you heard of the butterfly effect, {{userName}}-san?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-020","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"It's the idea that small phenomena such as a butterfly flapping its wings can affect the weather in a far away place...","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf04","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-021","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"I'm sorry, this is getting a little complicated, isn't it?","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"smile03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-022","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,"requirePlayEffect":0,"effectReferenceIdx":0,"requirePlaySound":0,"soundReferenceIdx":0,"whenStartHideWindow":0},{"talkCharacters":[{"characterId":18}],"windowDisplayName":"Chisato","body":"Simply put, it means that the small events of the past can later have a big impact on the future.","tention":0,"lipSyncMode":1,"motionChangeFactor":1,"motions":[{"characterId":18,"motionName":"nf03","expressionName":"default","timingSyncValue":0}],"voices":[{"characterId":18,"voiceId":"memorial138-023","volume":1}],"speed":0,"fontSize":0,"whenFinishCloseWindow":0,